{"tid":984173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"RMG 泰拳女上完堂嘔吐 昏迷送院搶救","createTime":"2019-01-16T14:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:14:40.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0d54daba0dfc97c79506b9991f02b3a4196d56","tid":984173,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190116/59151167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59151167&d=RTsWOQJ2NVSqFPKyJPBKg7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=67602be0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59151167&h=2134e649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190116/59151167</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角彌敦道798號健峰保險大廈一間健身中心，晚上7時許，一名年約20多歲姓蕭女子在健身中心學習泰拳，當上完第一節45分鐘的課堂後，蕭女表示不適，職員扶她坐下休息。未幾，蕭女衝入廁所嘔吐，然後暈倒，職員發現報案。救護員接報趕至，將她送往廣華醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547642371_4dc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547642371_4dc3.jpg&h=a498db3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80b695df60cb5cc970f6a84a1fe2ce6f970b6ef2","tid":984173,"uid":14916,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"女？"},{"pid":"6534c0a6c495d36422e0d877efd994d4fc898e96","tid":984173,"uid":40940,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"因為照左鏡？"},{"pid":"9c8bdc0fe6df61f6ca45fe57f73f5095e9f23715","tid":984173,"uid":94828,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"扺啦tb"},{"pid":"0e91ca1d3783e02f275917f02d00f8b4768a20b8","tid":984173,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:33:01.